title: Tech completes day one of Wes Kittley Invite - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech completes day one of Wes Kittley Invite - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: ABILENE, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team wrapped up day one of the Wes Kittley Invitational hosted by ACU at Elmer Gray Stadium Friday night.
